The Samson Manufacturing Evolution Series free float rails are customizable AR-15 handguards. The Evo rail attaches to a standard barrel nut with a two piece thermal bushing constructed of stainless steel, two locking tabs ensure the rail does not rotate under stress. The continuous top rail allows you to mount optics anywhere along the top of the rifle and allows same-plane iron sights to be mounted.
